sequenceDiagram
    participant Pipeline as TransformPipeline
    participant TP as TensorParallelPass
    participant EP as ExpertParallelPass
    participant GMM as ExpertGroupedMMPass
    participant CP as ContextParallelPass
    participant Recompute as Recompute/Offload
    participant Comm as CommInserterPass
    participant Fuse as FusionPass
    participant Analysis as Analysis Passes

    Pipeline->>TP: tp > 1 时运行
    Pipeline->>EP: ep > 1 时运行
    EP-->>Pipeline: expert 节点带 ep_needs_a2a
    Pipeline->>GMM: ep > 1 时运行
    GMM-->>Pipeline: expert 子图变为 GroupedMM / MegaMoE
    Pipeline->>CP: cp > 1 时运行
    Pipeline->>Recompute: training 时运行
    Pipeline->>Comm: TP/EP/CP 任一开启时运行
    Comm-->>Pipeline: 插入 all_reduce / all_to_all / CP 通信
    Pipeline->>Fuse: 通用 fusion
    Pipeline->>Analysis: FLOPs / Roofline / 通信时延
